data.description: Welcome to your renovated home, situated in a prime location near Bus Stops, the Light Rail, the Turnpike, the Bayonne Bridge and the Holland Tunnel.  This charming home offers the perfect balance of comfort and style and with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, there is enough room for everyone.  Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior, featuring an open floor plan that enhances the flow of natural light throughout the living spaces.  Other features include central air, a driveway, a front porch, a rear patio and a pool! This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Experience the perfect blend of urban living and suburban tranquility in this renovated gem by making your appointment today.
